{"tid":919200,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"應該要立法限制啲死肥撚坐車要俾兩個位錢","createTime":"2018-11-28T00:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T05:31:53.000Z","uid":21248,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9f0617e7b510e9e48b2dee1985dad7f816c68b89","tid":919200,"uid":21248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:59:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我啱啱坐埋最後一個窗口位<br />\n條肥撚就狗衝坐咗係我隔離 <br />\n佢一坐低我已經feel 到佢隻肥撚手臂逼鳩哂過黎<br />\n跟住唔知佢真訓定扮訓 隻手係咁sir 落我大脾<br />\nsir 完擺返落自己到唔夠2秒又sir 過 <br />\n最犀利係佢隻手已經擺埋係大脾中間都仲sir到過黎<br />\n我成程車右邊肌肉都繃到緊鳩哂 即刻早一個站落下層算<br />\n屌你老母一係你就俾多份錢 我俾你坐撚埋佢<br />\n一係你就搭的士 咪撚係到騷擾人<br />\n真係毀撚咗我一大朝早好心情"},{"pid":"b481d190d465eaee44110e314e46bf2576105f4e","tid":919200,"uid":91196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:01:09.000Z","msg":"所以我永遠坐出面個位 就係防止啲肥佬坐埋黎痴住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ac19cc3b38d0829fe8fcad6fb56890bfc2f76b","tid":919200,"uid":21248,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b481d190d465eaee44110e314e46bf2576105f4e","tid":919200,"uid":91196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:01:09.000Z","msg":"所以我永遠坐出面個位 就係防止啲肥佬坐埋黎痴住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:08:23.000Z","msg":"原來仲有呢招 但窗口位捱住好好訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce862d2c3430c6f85036e1c0bf612f251284d74f","tid":919200,"uid":55198,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:12:22.000Z","msg":"D肥人例牌坐個半位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n剩返半個位都唔知可以俾邊個坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時寧願企到腳斷都唔會坐埋D肥人度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為會逼到呼吸唔到， <br />\n同唔想同D肥人有身體接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"h